<p><span style="color: black"><strong>醇</strong></span><br />
<span style="color: black"><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rogerxiao" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5140328); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5140328&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663857" alt="RogerXiao" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5140328)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rogerxiao" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5140328); return false;">RogerXiao</a></span> 与 <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/timeelapsed" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3662783); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3662783&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663857" alt="TimeElapsed" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3662783)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/timeelapsed" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3662783); return false;">TimeElapsed</a></span></span></p>
<p><span style="color: red">（crossover：<a href="https://b23.tv/av64825756/p2">LeaF &amp; Optie &amp; Fiz - MARENOL</a>）</span></p>
<p><span style="color: black">本文为《看图说话-彼岸花》参赛作品。</span></p>
